net.sf.sprockets.google

Class Place

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.sprockets.google.Place
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImmutablePlace

    @Value.Immutable
public abstract class Place
extends Object
    Google Place returned from a Places method. The properties which are populated will vary according to the Places method called and the fields provided. placeId and primitive properties (when available) will always be populated. Properties that have not been populated will return null, an empty list, or the default primitive value specified in the method documentation.
